I ADORE this classic, the music, the comic silliness, but the little girl SLAYS me, and when I first saw this movie 25 years ago, i dreamed of one day having a daughter like this one! I did end up with a wonderful daughter, who finally got to watch Los Tres Huastecos with me. I had the idea of looking for it online, found it, ordered it and it arrived 2 days later. It has subtitles if you don't know Spanish. Great seller, great product!!
Arrived within a couple of days. Bought it as a gift for my father-in-law. Loved it!
